FuncDecl.Name: GuiVirtualDataGrid
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Create a data grid control in virtual mode.</summary> <param name="themeName">The theme name for retriving a default control template.</param> <param name="_itemProvider">The item provider for this control.</param> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SetViewToDefault
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Change the view to data grid's default view.</summary> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: GetSelectedCell
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Get the row index and column index of the selected cell.</summary> <returns>The row index and column index of the selected cell.</returns> </Document>

FuncDecl.Name: SelectCell
FuncDecl.Document: <Document> <summary>Select a cell.</summary> <returns>Returns true if the editor is opened.</returns> <param name="value">The row index and column index of the selected cell.</param> <param name="openEditor">Set to true to open an editor.</param> </Document>
